Text: Installation gave an error. AVG reported several viruses. 5 programs installed onto my hardrive in the background: BucksBee Loyatly Plugin, FULL - DISKfighter, PricePeep, SearchAmong Toolbar and VIO Player.
Also, MalwareBytes reported 2 problems in the system folder after installation. One called systemupdate.exe and another with random letters.
Thanks for the heads up, kaz, I won't be downloading this, cheers.
